   {
      "body" : "I agree with @sipa.\r\nAlso, I think a such radical API change would be dangerous. It could make sense if we would introduce a co-existign v2 API (where you may can disabled the v1 API). But to do that for just the floating point issue (that has no guarantees to make it safer as @sipa stated) is probably not worth the effort.",
